Class InputMap

java.lang.Object

              com.esri.gpt.catalog.schema.InputMap

public class InputMap
extends Input

Interactive map component.

The component is configured from a node with a schema configuration XML document.

Example:

<parameter key="envelope.map">
<input type="map"/>
</parameter>
